.\"O If any of
.\"O .SM
.\"O .BR RANDOM ,
.\"O .SM
.\"O .BR SECONDS ,
.\"O .SM
.\"O .BR LINENO ,
.\"O .SM
.\"O .BR HISTCMD ,
.\"O .SM
.\"O .BR FUNCNAME ,
.\"O .SM
.\"O .BR GROUPS ,
.\"O or
.\"O .SM
.\"O .B DIRSTACK
.\"O are unset, they lose their special properties, even if they are
